schemas.name: AMRAP
schemas.description: As Many Rounds As Possible in a set time

schemas.name: EMOM
schemas.description: Complete as many reps of the excercise as you can in one minute, then switch to the next and repeat.
Ascending ladder of reps increasing by 5, start with 5 reps of each excercise then 10 and so on.

schemas.name: Ascending Ladder
schemas.description: Ascending ladder of reps increasing by 1, start with 1 reps of each excercise then 2 and so on until time runs out.
